snippet.description:
This immersive sandbox detective stealth game from ColePowered Games and Fireshine Games left Early Access on 26th Sep, as announced exclusively during the Convergence Showcase. Watch creators take on its fully simulated sci-fi noir city of crime and corruption.

Buy now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/986130

